   $(document).ready(function () {
             $(document).pngFix();

                 if ($('.slideshows').children().length > 0) {
                     $('.slideshows').before('<div id="nav" class="nav">').cycle({
                         fx: 'fade', // choose your transition type, ex: fade, scrollUp, shuffle, etc...
                         pager: '#nav',
                         timeout: 8000,
                         before: function () { if (window.console) console.log(this.src); }
                     });
                     $('#pausa').click(function () {
                         $('.slideshows').cycle('pause');
                         $('#play').removeClass("invisible");
                         $(this).addClass("invisible");
                     });
 
                     $('#play').click(function () {
                         $('.slideshows').cycle('resume');
                         $('#pausa').removeClass("invisible");
                         $(this).addClass("invisible");
                     });
                 }
             }
 
 
             try {
                 jQuery('#carousel_inner').carousel('#simplePrevious', '#simpleNext');
             } catch (err) { }
 
 
             //08/11/2011 MEXDFUEN 7738 
             function queryString(parameter) {
                 var loc = location.search.substring(1, location.search.length);
                 var param_value = false;
                 var params = loc.split("&");
                 for (i = 0; i < params.length; i++) {
                     param_name = params[i].substring(0, params[i].indexOf('='));
                     if (param_name == parameter) {
                         param_value = params[i].substring(params[i].indexOf('=') + 1)
                     }
                 }
                 if (param_value) {
                     return param_value;
                 }
                 else {
                     return false; //Here determine return if no parameter is found
                 }
             }
 
             updateBackgroundImage();
             if (typeof handleError === "function") {
                 handleError();
             }
 
             });
             $('#logo_link').click(function () {
                 location.replace("Default.aspx");
 
             });
 
             try {
                 $('.link_tooltip').qtip({
                     content: $('#tool_infoabo').html(),
                     hide: { when: 'inactive', delay: 1000 },
                     position: { corner: { target: 'bottomMiddle', tooltip: 'topMiddle' } }
                 });
             } catch (err) { }
           
 
         //MEXCTOVA
         function timming(date, title) {
             // set the date we're counting down to
             $("#spanTimmingTitle").text(title)
             var arrDate = date.split("/");
             var datemonth = arrDate[0]
             var dateDay = arrDate[1]
             var dateYear = arrDate[2]
             var finDate = dateYear + '/' + (datemonth) + '/' + dateDay
             var target_date = new Date(finDate).getTime();
             
             // variables for time units
             var days, hours, minutes, seconds;
 
             // update the tag with id "countdown" every 1 second
             setInterval(function () {
 
                 // find the amount of "seconds" between now and target
                 var current_date = new Date().getTime();
                 var seconds_left = (target_date - current_date) / 1000;
 
                 // do some time calculations
                 days = parseInt(seconds_left / 86400);
                 seconds_left = seconds_left % 86400;
 
                 hours = parseInt(seconds_left / 3600);
                 seconds_left = seconds_left % 3600;
 
                 minutes = parseInt(seconds_left / 60);
                 seconds = parseInt(seconds_left % 60);
 
                 // format countdown string + set tag value
                 if (days != 0 || hours != 0 || minutes != 0 || seconds != 0) {
                     $("#spanTimmingDays").text('' + days);
                     $("#spanTimmingHrs").text('' + hours);
                     $("#spanTimmingMin").text('' + minutes);
                     $("#spanTimmingSeg").text('' + seconds);
                 }
 
                
 
             }, 1000);
         }
  </script>

             var n;
             var evento = window.event || elEvento
             n = evento.keyCode;
             if (n == 0) { n = evento.charCode }//Mozilla  
             if (n == 9 || n == 8 || n == 37 || n == 39 || (n > 47 & n < 58))
             { return true; }
             return false;
